			"96": "<sup class=\"versenum\">96 </sup>I have seen a limit to all perfection,but your commandment is exceedingly <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-15995EN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference EN&quot;&gt;EN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-15995EN\"></sup>broad.",
