			"98": "<sup class=\"versenum\">98 </sup>Your commandment makes me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-15997EQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference EQ&quot;&gt;EQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-15997EQ\"></sup>wiser than my enemies,for it is ever with me.",
