			"101": "<sup class=\"versenum\">101 </sup>I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16000EU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference EU&quot;&gt;EU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16000EU\"></sup>hold back my feet from every evil way,in order to keep your word.",
