			"114": "<sup class=\"versenum\">114 </sup>You are my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16013FO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference FO&quot;&gt;FO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16013FO\"></sup>hiding place and my <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16013FP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference FP&quot;&gt;FP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16013FP\"></sup>shield;I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-ESV-16013FQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference FQ&quot;&gt;FQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-ESV-16013FQ\"></sup>hope in your word.",
